question: Dau-hinn ê hō͘-koaⁿ tī Tē-2 Keng-chè-ōe ê tòe-tiûⁿ piáu-hiān, kap in tī Tē-4 Keng-chè-ōe ê tòe-tiûⁿ siōng hó ê piáu-hiān, ūi-hē-chóaⁿ ū kāng hāng?
answer: Tī Tē-4 Keng-chè-ōe, chhiam-tūi ê tòe-tiûⁿ siōng hó ê piáu-hiān sī chin chē pái tit-tio̍h 'Kok-ka Pòaⁿ-koâⁿ-sài' (2003, 2005, 2006 nî). Tī Tē-2 Keng-chè-ōe, in siōng hó ê sêng-chiū sī tī 1999 nî tit-tio̍h 'Khu Chhú-koaⁿ', chha-īⁿ chin tōa.

question: Tī kó-chē ê kùi-chiat, tī Tâi-Tōa 4 hun-cho̍h tńg-lâi tō bōe tit-tio̍h Playoffs ê khó-lêng?
Tī USL PDL cháⁿ-chū liâm-á, hit-ê siâⁿ-chúi ê sài-chhin, teh tē 1 miâ ê Open Cup tû-chiap kiat-kó sī sím-mih?
Tùi 1997 kàu 2000 nî, chit ê tūi tī USISL/USL A-League ê sî-chūn, in Open Cup pâi-chhut ê chìn-tiân sī chūn-chāi ná-piáⁿ?
answer: Tī chit tōaⁿ sî-ki, chit ê tūi ê Open Cup pâi-chhut kòe-têng sī bô chún-tēng. 1997 nî bē-tàng pâi-chhut liáu-āu, in tit-tio̍h chha-put-to iân-chū ê siōng-hó ê sêng-chek, lâi kàu 3 hôe. Kàu 1999 nî tō kó͘-tóe kàu 2 hôe, chiū-chāi 2000 nî koh bē-tàng pâi-chhut, bô kiàn-kò͘ ê chìn-tiân chhuat-chāi.

question: Chiah-sī ū siâⁿ-muí ū sî-chūn, chiàⁿ-chòe tī 'USL PDL' liân-bêng, koh tī playoff tit-tioh 'National Semifinals'?
Tī chhú-liám ê chóng-kiat-sò͘ ê sìⁿ-khuán tiong, ū chūi-chē pái-su̍t ê sè-kài-koan tit-tio̍h liân-sai chham-ka ê chē-chē?

Nāi kóng, nā-sī sài-seng ê sêng-chiap thang-oân lâi kóng, ài kàu "Conference Finals" he̍k-chiá khah-hó, hit-ê sî, tiō-sī 1999 nî ê "Conference Quarterfinals" ū thiam-ka kàu "Conference Finals" ê sî, chiū-kóng niû-á ū-kúi-ê sêng-chiap ê sî-kan lâi kóng?
Tui chiᴀnn-á ê hun-kip (Division) kap in chiap-piah ê kong-tâi (playoffs) ū bē-suan ê koan-hē bē? Ū bat chiap-piah kong-tâi bē?
answer: Ū, chu-liāu sī hō͘ lâng khòaⁿ-chhut, tī b lower ê Division 4 ê sî, chiᴀnn-á koh-khah ū khó-lêng chiap-piah kong-tâi. In tī Division 4 ê sî, ū 45.5% ê sai-chhun (5 chū 11) chiap-piah kah, pí hō͘ Division 2 ê sî (4 chū 1) kan-na 25% koh-khah cao. Che sī kóng-bêng tī b lower ê hun-kip, in koh-khah ē tit-tio̍h sêng-chiàⁿ.

question: Tī 'Playoffs' kap 'Open Cup' chit nn̄g kiat ê lia̍t-toaⁿ lāi-bīn, nā thâi chhut bô kâng ê kiat-kó ê hāng-m̄-sī, to̍h-sī `Open Cup` koh khah chió ê o̍h?
Ùi USL PDL (2001-2011) ê sî-tsūn, nánda nî-tè sī siōng giâ-khì tò-lâi ê tîng-tōo siōng bē hò--ê sū-ê li̍p-pia̍h?
Jī-tang ê playoff tāi-piáu siōng hó?
